NAME

Class::Mix - dynamic class mixing

DESCRIPTION

The "mix_class" function provided by this module dynamically generates
`anonymous' classes with specified inheritance.

INSTALLATION

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

